name: President Ron DeSantis
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: During the 2024 Presidential race, an ERC20 meme token named $RON was created by supporters of President DeSantis, reflecting an integration of digital culture into the campaign. This meme token symbolizes their commitment to technological innovation, further amplified by Elon Musk's endorsement of President DeSantis via Twitter spaces. The $RON token serves to foster a sense of community and stimulates online discussions, enhancing the visibility of the campaign. This innovative strategy, leveraging blockchain technology, promotes both fundraising and supporter engagement while advocating for a tech-forward approach in governance.
